									<td class="blog_tag">
																			<span class="SG_txtb">标签：</span>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%B9%C5%CC%EC%98%B7&by=tag" target="_blank">古天樂</a></h3>
